            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31559759/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31559759/" class="">第23页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chenshi819/" class=" " title="Focus！">Focus！</a>
                (知足，感恩。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31559759">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">也都能勾画出一份对日本铁道的遐想：穿着校服的青春少年，车窗外的夏日树荫，古老小站，精致可口的便当，甚至一段干净悲伤的纯爱故事。这是铁道上的国家——习惯用速度来写就文明史和奋斗史，用铁轨连接时间和空间。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-11 16:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>也都能勾画出一份对日本铁道的遐想：穿着校服的青春少年，车窗外的夏日树荫，古老小站，精致可口的便当，甚至一段干净悲伤的纯爱故事。这是铁道上的国家——习惯用速度来写就文明史和奋斗史，用铁轨连接时间和空间。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31559759/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2014-05-11 16:13
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
